IN THOSE QUIET MOMENTS
AFTER THE STORM...

42:15.263 --> 42:17.535
(electricity crackling
and popping)

42:17.535 --> 42:20.308
DO WE LEARN...

42:20.308 --> 42:23.842
WHO WAS STRONG ENOUGH...

42:23.842 --> 42:25.013
TO SURVIVE IT?

